Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.13,0:00:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看電視時房間要明亮\N而且要保持適當的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢欣賞完結篇喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.88,0:00:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美要守護主人的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.39,0:00:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了，這樣就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.87,0:00:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.81,0:00:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.25,0:01:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美要守護...主人的夢想...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.42,0:01:03.72,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,威力十足的奇蹟就要發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.43,0:01:10.12,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,瞬息萬變的魔法太美妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.53,0:01:15.43,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,抒情的奇蹟\N因愛而陶醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.57,0:01:18.20,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因為久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.84,0:01:30.68,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,有從KISS開始的奇蹟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.25,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不論是雨天晴天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.39,0:01:36.79,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有你所以我能大步向前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.92,0:01:42.86,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我長了翅膀\N變成天使飛了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.00,0:01:49.13,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在銀河彼岸閃亮的教堂裡\N敲響婚禮的鍾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.27,0:01:52.14,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不會擔心，不要在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.27,0:01:55.17,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,哭泣是因為喜悅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.31,0:01:58.21,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,我會用我的懷抱守護著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.34,0:02:01.61,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.52,0:02:07.38,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,威力十足的奇蹟就要發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.52,0:02:10.42,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,瞬息萬變的魔法太美妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.56,0:02:13.53,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,抒情的奇蹟\N因愛而陶醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.66,0:02:16.53,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因為久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.66,0:02:19.69,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因為久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.02,0:02:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"臨兵斗者皆陣列在前..."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.62,0:02:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岬還說要讓鋼鐵天使自由\N她們居然在自相殘殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.52,0:02:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"臨兵斗者皆陣列在前..."\N不行，我們的法術完全沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.96,0:02:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"臨兵斗者皆陣列在前..."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我心跳的好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.06,0:03:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道能不能好好演奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.50,0:03:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人的大提琴最棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.58,0:03:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了久留美我要好好演奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.95,0:03:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有媽媽，沙希，卡玲加\N也為了小潤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要為了大家全力以赴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,23號的神維那己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.93,0:03:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請准備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.79,0:03:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐，姐姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，她還真難纏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們快去會場\N那己快開始演奏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.34,0:04:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐，你醒一醒，姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.08,0:04:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.86,0:04:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是23號的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.30,0:04:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桃樹學園中學部神維那己同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.58,0:04:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美...大家...仔細聽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.64,0:05:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了，好像已經開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.58,0:05:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣不好吧，那己也在裡面耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不讓她去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不讓她去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.90,0:05:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.87,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行...小潤小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.88,0:05:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣主人會傷心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的夢想會破滅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一點都不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們再也不能像從前一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不在乎嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.16,0:06:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.39,0:06:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N我更不希望主人的夢想消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.47,0:06:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美不想看到悲傷的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說得這麼好聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.67,0:06:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美...久留美...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.41,0:06:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望主人永遠保持笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美希望主人永遠微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.26,0:07:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的\N從大家身上得到很多東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.46,0:07:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我無法報答大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.43,0:07:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少能藉著大提琴\N表達我的謝意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.00,0:08:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們聽吧\N我為你們拉奏的大提琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.76,0:08:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了...\N主人的大提琴聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美都聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.33,0:08:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想完成主人的夢想\N希望大家也能了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.45,0:08:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼光球?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是姐姐的天使心...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.90,0:09:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是就是岬說的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.10,0:09:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.90,0:09:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這個光球又怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.91,0:09:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓久留美了解\N我的感情比她還要深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.91,0:09:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.91,0:09:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，請你住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.85,0:09:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在阻礙那己小姐的話\N以後一定會後悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.16,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想永遠跟那己在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小潤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.27,0:09:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小潤，怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.24,0:09:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有沒有進步呢\N你說啊，小潤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.22,0:09:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.15,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你們不說我也了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.59,0:10:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我就是無法祝福那己\N完成她的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.20,0:10:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我一直也不坦誠...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.21,0:10:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始宣布本大賽的優勝者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.14,0:10:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,參賽號碼23號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.51,0:10:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桃樹學園國中部的\N神維那己同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.89,0:10:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美，太好了，我得獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.83,0:10:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，不愧是我的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.43,0:10:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是久留美，還有大家的支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你怎麼這個樣子...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服弄得髒兮兮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.14,0:10:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我來這裡的路上\N不小心跌倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.51,0:10:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭禧你，那己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.24,0:10:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小潤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.41,0:10:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你穿得好酷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點太搶眼了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.25,0:11:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，你總算能實現夢想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.25,0:11:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，不過才剛到達夢想的入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.12,0:11:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，真的...真的太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.33,0:11:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人\N去國外之後也要努力往前沖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有要去國外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.37,0:11:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.74,0:11:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是為了留學\N才參加大賽的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.44,0:11:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N只有高中生才有留學資格啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.75,0:11:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我本來就不想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.78,0:11:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想跟大家在一起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.22,0:11:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啾，主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊，久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.32,0:11:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，久留美姐姐動作真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.59,0:11:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開她，久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.06,0:11:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人只屬於久留美一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美姐姐太自私了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.07,0:11:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要來攪局，喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.67,0:11:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，不可以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超級無敵"哎呀呀"的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.91,0:12:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我太高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.05,0:12:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啾啾啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.97,0:12:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人\N希望今天也是快樂的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.41,0:12:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啾啾啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.18,0:12:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第12話 清澄的藍天另一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.98,0:12:47.36,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,相信夢想\N相信天使會降臨心靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.49,0:12:54.56,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,所以隨時抬頭看看天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.93,0:13:01.67,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,可以輕輕打開眼睛之窗嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.91,0:13:08.68,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,可以輕輕傾聽我的心聲嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.82,0:13:16.58,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,因為很喜歡你靦腆的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.72,0:13:22.85,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,今天比昨天\N明天比今天更愛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.73,0:13:26.66,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,只要一下下就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.50,0:13:30.56,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能接近夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.70,0:13:39.13,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,想與有著天使翅膀的你飛舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.28,0:13:46.08,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的，純樸的女孩\N卻是一心一意的認真女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.22,0:13:53.12,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的，害羞的女孩\N卻是積極樂觀的眼鏡女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.26,0:13:56.92,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey Honey Honey
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.06,0:14:03.63,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,一定能飛向清澄的藍天